        public static java.lang.Class getJavaClass(java.lang.String type)
        Translates a data type from a schema to the corresponding Java data type. If no match is found, null is returned.
        Parameters:
        type - The name (string) of the data type as specified in the schema
        Returns:
        A Java data type that corresponds to data type mentioned in the schema. If no matching type is found, null is returned.
